# Briefs stay local-only by default — they're workstream-scoped
# drafts that get superseded as work evolves. Exception:
# handoff-load-bearing briefs are explicitly allowed below.
# (Pattern note: must be docs/briefs/* not docs/briefs/ — git cannot
# re-include a file via negation if the parent directory itself is
# excluded.)
docs/briefs/*
!docs/briefs/SIMPLE_PIPELINE_BRIEF_v2.md
